    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation level for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 1. The overall credibility evidence is judged sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision for the Class II CPB device hemolysis prediction.",
